<br>
EQ... now sucks.... it's too easy, dumbed down, and on top of that they fiddle with the gameplay WAY too much.  At the end, I felt like I was living in a virtual dictatorship, oppressed, while I am merely trying to enjoy myself, for my 13 bucks a month.  <br>
<br>
